gameplay  1010 team fotress 2 is an critically acclaim shooter that takes some of its formular from a fastpaced games such as quake & unreal tournament it is considered to be one of the best free 2 play games ever made next to dota 2 did i not mentioned that these two games is published by valve  yup anything that valve made is a masterpiece the game had a total of nine classes ranging from sniperdemomanscoutheavyengineersoldierpyromedic & spy each of the classes had their own role and different play style each of the classes had their own charming personality and likeable characteristics you can also taunt to kill your enemy if you are lucky the games provide a massive tons of modes and it rare to see in a first person shooter game just look at these list  httpwikiteamfortresscomwikilist_of_game_modes you get numerous weapondifferent parts of outfits as you play through many matches there is also a crafting system where you combined different parts of weapon & scrap to obtained a much more powerful weapon each of the weapon provides different types of ability & stats most of it have their own pros & cons the game requires a lot of teamwork sometimes depending on what modes you are playing also medic  heavy  ownage graphics  1010 for a game that come out in 2007it age extremely well and still to these days the cartoonish artstyle impress me a lot a lot of the texture are well details as well as the character models each of the maps provide different variety of background & well thought out level design the animations perform from each character are well done and doesnt look like crap this game also have blood & gore in it too and it is pretty well detailed too audio  1010 the soundtrack for this game is superb especially the main theme songs all of them are done in an orchestral theme while they dont go for a realistic sound effects since it doesnt fit in with the game themethey go for a much more funny approach in making all of sound effects that really blend in with the feels of the games the voice acting for each of the classes is excellent  except for pyro cause he mostly mumble random stuff  each of them have their own unique taunts & quote longlasting appeal  1010 this games provides more modes than any first person shooter game does along with an ongoing update with every 23 weeks or so there is a huge amount of items you collect during your gameplay sessions not to mentioned there is a bunch of custom map that you download & play on it even much more fun if you have friends to play with you adding a ton of enjoyment into the game you will never get bored with each of the class since there is always a challenge when dealing with certain type of situation not to mentioned the amount of achievement you can get just by playing the game is huge so this will keep you busy for a long times final verdict  1010 really recommended for everyone especially to those who are not a fan of first person shooter game every game that valve made have their own special momentsinnovative gameplay & unique style a truly masterpiece of arts grade  s  masterpiece 
