team fortress 2 the game where everyone loves hats but hates newcomers actual review hello everyone im here to tell ya about tf2 its one of valves biggest games out there maybe not up there in competitiveness like dota or csgo but its more of a game you grab a couple of beers with your friends and just have fun the weapons are not like this stupid reach this level to unlock this op weapon thats meta as all heck no in tf2 you find weapons just through playing the game now some would argue that this is a bad system but to counter this the weapons you start with the stock weapons are the best weapons in the game no downsides on upsides sits completly balanced now in each shooter game you have this generic story about a marine taking on a army or this superpowered soldier but in tf2 there is no single player camapign which might turn you off but what it makes up for is frantic action and hilrious characters seriously tf2 pushes the boundaries of fpscharacters every character in this game is a stereotype like the scout for example hes form boston ergo hes annoying loves baseball and is generally really cocky but valve made it work so that hes completly funny same with all characters even the mann of espionnage himself the spy theres also holiday themed events like the scream fortress update every halloween smissmass every christmas etc tf2 goes out of its way to have microdlc like hats taunts even the weapons from earlier you can buy but they aint cheap only bad thing i can say about this game is the community they are really hard on new players my advice hop onto the tutorial and do all 4 of them it will give you a general sense of how to play tf2 also sports a coop game mode called mann vs machine its like tower defense except you and 5 other players are defending your base from a bomb that robotic versions of the classes are carrying you can do it for free with your buds or buy a ticket and do tours everyones after the fabelled australium weapons which are golden weapons that go for alot of money so if your willing to have rng hate or love you try it out in conclusion tf2 has so much things modern day fpss dont have if you havent tried tf2 yet what are you doing its free forever go download it maggot
