team fortress 2 is a simply phenomenal title if youre looking for a free to play first person shooter it has nine classes which are distinctly different in how they look and play and there are dozens upon dozens of weapons you can unlock either through simply playing the game and getting free drops crafting them earning certain items through achievements or trading other players for them these unlocks can further change the way you play a class allowing for even more variety one class has the ability to be a bomb wielding maniac or use a magic head collecting sword and shield to slice off heads there are 50 official maps and 10 different game modes variety is the spice of life and team fortress 2 certainly has variety it can be daunting to get into considering just how much there is to learn but its worth the investment
