ayed in game to show off to everyone youve participated in a very special coin again another feature thats unique to our game we really tried our hardest to make a unique first person shooter experience in our new game counter fortresss global teamfensive the sequel we hope you enjoy the game that hits you this summer me ah urh ok thanks for your time um gabe i look forward to when you announce half life 3 sometime in the next decade lord gabe dont worry my friend thats never going to happen me you cruel man how could you do this  end of interview here  unfortunately thats all i could get on counter fortresss global teamfensive the sequel cfgt and half life 3 before gaben called the illuminati and threw me out but i hope this is enough for you steam readers 1 like  1 prayer for half life 3
