so the infamous team fortress 2 the game has been around for a long time 8 years to be exact and was first brought out on xbox 360 as a bundle the orange box still to this day the game has a large community keeping the game alive this game is a huge benefactor in the trading community and is constantly having various updates to the game for new items and refreshes to keep the game going as most of you already know team fortress 2 is a multiplayer fps with an objective to defeat the opposing side been blu or red depending on what side you are on throughout various types of game modes the class system consists of 9 characters to pick from 1 scout a fast agile character primarilly played to get into the enemy base and capturesteal the intellegence 2 soldier a slow but strong character weilding a rocket launcher he is played to be offensive and support the team by killing everyone basically 3 pyro played to be offensive and spy check so the spy does not get into your back line and take out your team and sentries etc 4 demoman a slow character played to support your team by getting into the back line and drop bombs everywhere and destroy their defences and keep the enemies in their spawn 5 heavy the heavy is a very slow charcter but to make up for this he weilds a minigun and has a tonne of heath you guessed it he just sits there as a tank and kills and defends as he pleases 6 engineer the engineer is solely a defensive character who supports the team he is very versitile he builds sentries to defend sets up teleporters and has a dispenser which regrenerates heath and stocks up on ammo for nearby friendlies 7 medic as the name says the medic is a support and runs around healing your team pretty straight forward 8 sniper now the sniper sits back and defends with his rifle this character can take out anyone with a single shot making him a valuable asset to any team 9 spy the spy supports the team greatly by getting into the back line and to take out the engineers gear doin