warning this game is most fun when you know your  at least halfway and have some experience it may be repelling at first this is a incredibly fun and addictive fps the graphics are stylized in a cartoonish fashion making this one of the most recognizable games the maps are very welldesigned which is something valve always gives us i guess some introduction to the gameplay would be nice so here you go the gameplay centers around 9 classes each with a unique playstyle and different skills required to play this class efficiently every with their own weaknesses and strengths only full cooperation between the usually 12 players will bring victory to the team you have to know your  or be called a noob this can be solved by reading guides completing tutorials and simply practicing on public servers you need to get into the mood to play a class which can easily be achieved by simply playing it for a while something important to note is that there is no campaign but offline practice does exist the community is incredibly active nothing more can be said you can download custom models sounds and even huds some people may say its pay to win this just isnt true the items in the store are used only to earn respect and dont effect gameplay at all while weapons are buyable its completely pointless to buy them there you can get it randomly literally anytime or by trading i guarantee that if you go on a full 32player trade server someone will own the weapon youre looking for and wont ask much for it at all i have never had so much fun playing a multiplayerbased communityfueled game ps dont play as sniper snipers are cowards pps codsucks
