silly review i tried quitting this game after hundreds of hours turns out i just took a break serious review its an amazing fps game with heavy emphasis on mobility and teamwork there are various game modes and 9 classes with strengths and weaknesses meaning you have to work together you could do almost a chart that shows who trumps who naturally speaking any class can take any class if there is enough skill such as spy trumps sniper trumps pyro trumps spy going back to mobility if you pick this game up now i suggest heavily you learn mechanics of the game such as rocket jumping even as the slowest classes ex heavy you never want to stop moving meaning there is more skill than just shoot thing with gun along side this is the abundance of weapons and gamemodes meaning that if you ever get a feeling the game is growing stale just mix it up a bit and its almost a whole new game if all else fails there are various usermade gamemodes such as vs saxton hale to keep you entertained and despite its age this game looks really good and each character has amazing personality giving a great sense in charm something that lacks in the majority of fps games consider the age of this game and that its still a heavily played game you can see that its worth playing in terms of issues though there are some problems such as some slightly unbalanced weapons though this makes up a minority of them this game is also at this point largely playermade as well the majority of servers arent even owned by valve and most added content are supplied by players overall great game worth playing and getting addicted to but do not expect your everday shooter
